node.text:
Har Ghar Shiksha🇮🇳
Happy Independence Day ❤️
Coming soon!

It doesn’t matter where you are now, what matters is where you are going.

I was in Class 11th when I saw him in his first Seminar on YouTube. 8 years later I got the opportunity to be a guest on his platform.

He gave me a warm welcome and we had a great chat after the session.  He is very organized in his life and is very punctual.

His little daughter made a special gift for me - an adorable self drawn card.

Love to all the people who are hustling to achieve their dreams and goals❤️

Aasan Hai!

Last night I was standing on my rooftop and was watching the city. Just like I used to do in college.

The view reminds me about how big the world is and how small my problems are. It reminds me that I am just a small part of this big machine but also gives me hope - ki abhi to aur bahut phoda jaa sakta hai.

Walk alone if needed, be foolish, make mistakes, be disruptive.

Believe your gut, challenge yourself.
Why be good or great when you can be Unstoppable!
 
Tu Phodega🔥

First Golden Hat-Trick in India 🇮🇳 in Teaching (3 Gold and 6 Silver Play Buttons)

Anna, system change karna padega❤️

Pura North se lekar south tak!

Big Reveal on 12th October🔥
Aana Zaroor ❤️

(on Apna College channel)

The woods are lonely, dark & deep.
but I have a promise to keep

Happy Dussehra to you all❤️ 
I hope you & your family is healthy.

Getting ready to meet you all. First time in Chennai ❤️

Recently my father has been hospitalized. Seeing your father in pain in a hospital is a bad feeling. Family and Health are the most important. Our Parents have done way too much for us.
My father always says - Chinta chita samaan hoti hai
I wish that you all do so great in Life ki aaj se 20 saal baad aapko ye na lage ki kaash mai apne parents ke liye kuch aur kar pata (that I could have done better for my parents)

2.5Million Learners❤️🙏🏻
5 Lakh students joined us in almost 2months🪴
It would have not been possible without the constant Love and Support from you all. 
Love you all Apna College Army🔥
#hargharshiksha

In Life Focus on the Positives. 
Capture the Good Memories
